casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Hamilton.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hamilton (1990), 50 Ohio St. 3d 608.]

(No. 90-408 Submitted March 28, 1990 Decided April 11, 1990.)

The resignation of David A. Hamilton as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
